    <item>
      <title>Get the user locale from http headers</title>
      <link>https://kinnrot.github.io/get-user-locale-from-http-headers/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2014 07:42:00 -0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kinnrot.github.io/get-user-locale-from-http-headers/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you want to provide default localization support for guest user in your website yo can locate their browser locale by the following code:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color: #2b2b2b; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid; border-width: 0.01mm; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 100%; padding: 4px;&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;border: 0.01mm solid rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; line-height: 100%;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #cc7833;&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt; extract_locale_from_header&lt;br /&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #cc7833;&#34;&gt;unless&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt; request.env[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #a5c261;&#34;&gt;&amp;lsquo;HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE&amp;rsquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt;].nil?&lt;br /&gt;      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #cc7833;&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt; request.env[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #a5c261;&#34;&gt;&amp;lsquo;HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE&amp;rsquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt;].scan(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #a5c261;&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt;^[a-z]{2}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #a5c261;&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt;).first&lt;br /&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #cc7833;&#34;&gt;end&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #a5c261;&#34;&gt;&amp;lsquo;en&amp;rsquo;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e6e1dc;&#34;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #cc7833;&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This way you can determine on server side the locale of the user currently entered your site.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
